      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior upholstery, reflects a standard of care typically reserved for private collections. Mechanically superlative and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this specimen offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
